{
  "stem": "979.4",
  "chunk_idx": 16,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "The orchestra was separated-- some here, some there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And they put us to work.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I-- we had to be-- you know, to put things for the planes that they do-- made of cellophane, whatever they use it for.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had to do some kind of a, you know, like this, making things for the plane, like making up like a plait-- a plait-- whatever they say when they wore-- you wear in the hair-- when they make plaits.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So anyway, see, we were doing it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we were trying to throw it-- the most of it in the oven, you know, when we were working there.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then we saw somebody coming.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We slide needle in the door.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We say-- we start working.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So there, my sister was coming to work one day, and she fell.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She fell and she broke her leg.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And she was behind me, I didn't even know she was.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] I was-- when they told me you're sister is in the hospital.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I say, what's the matter?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So I went running there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "She says the ice.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "She-- she-- you know, she-- she slipped in the ice.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So, and then they put her in a hospital across from us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they were not taking good care of her.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And she was crying.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "She was telling me-- I could hear her through the wires.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "She was saying, she says, please get me out of here.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Please.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I'm gonna die here.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So I asked one of the singers who was a German Jew.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I say, please, can you ask Kramer?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Kramer knew us.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "You see, they became the commandants, and Irma Grese, in that camp-- there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "She-- like there were in Auschwitz, they became there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So-- They went to Belsen, also.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To Belsen.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
